                                        <h2>The Medicality Difference</h2>
                                        <p class="section__intro">
                                                We immerse ourselves in your culture and redefine service from within. Here‚Äôs what makes our approach unique:
                                        </p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="cards three-up">
                                        <article class="card">
                                                <div class="icon">ü§ù</div>
                                                <h3>Dual Focus on People</h3>
                                                <p>
                                                        We elevate patient satisfaction by first uplifting your care teams. By treating employee morale and culture as the foundation, five-star service is delivered consistently at every level.
                                                </p>
                                        </article>
                                        <article class="card">
                                                <div class="icon">üß≠</div>
                                                <h3>Embedded Transformation</h3>
                                                <p>
                                                        Our experts embed within your hospital for 6‚Äì12 months, working hand-in-hand with your staff. We implement new systems and behaviors in real time so change is sustainable and measurable.
                                                </p>
                                        </article>
                                        <article class="card">
                                                <div class="icon">‚ú®</div>
                                                <h3>Five-Star Service Standards</h3>
                                                <p>
                                                        We translate proven luxury hospitality protocols into clinical settings‚Äîfrom personalized greetings to immediate service recovery‚Äîso every patient feels the difference.
                                                </p>
                                        </article>
                                </div>
                        </section>

                        <section id="services" class="section services">
                                <div class="section__header">
                                        <p class="eyebrow">What We Do</p>
                                        <h2>Comprehensive Services</h2>
                                        <p class="section__intro">Consulting built for hospital leaders who expect measurable, lasting change.</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="cards three-up">
                                        <article class="card service-card">
                                                <div class="icon">üõéÔ∏è</div>
                                                <h3>Hospitality-Inspired Process Redesign</h3>
                                                <p>
                                                        We overhaul key processes from pre-arrival to post-discharge, infusing best practices from iconic hotels at every step of the patient journey.
                                                </p>
                                        </article>
                                        <article class="card service-card">
                                                <div class="icon">üéì</div>
                                                <h3>Empathy-Driven Staff Training</h3>
                                                <p>
                                                        Executive-to-frontline training programs focused on empathy, communication, and service excellence create cohesive, trusted teams.
                                                </p>
                                        </article>
                                        <article class="card service-card">
                                                <div class="icon">üåø</div>
                                                <h3>Employee Experience Consulting</h3>
                                                <p>
                                                        We strengthen the employee lifecycle‚Äîhiring, onboarding, retention, and growth‚Äîto build cultures where caregivers feel valued and energized.
                                                </p>
                                        </article>
                                </div>
                                <div class="cta-banner">
                                        <div>
                                                <p class="eyebrow">Ready to elevate?</p>
                                                <h3>Bring five-star service to your hospital.</h3>
                                                <p>Let‚Äôs design a bespoke roadmap that marries clinical excellence with luxury-level hospitality.</p>
                                        </div>
                                        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#contact">Start the Conversation</a>
                                </div>
                        </section>

                        <section id="contact" class="section contact">
                                <div class="contact__content">
                                        <div class="contact__intro">
                                                <p class="eyebrow">Contact Us</p>
                                                <h2>Start the Transformation</h2>
                                                <p class="lead">Ready to elevate your patient experience? Let‚Äôs discuss how The Medicality can bring five-star service to your organization.</p>
                                                <div class="contact__details">
                                                        <p><strong>Email:</strong> info@themedicality.com</p>
                                                        <p><strong>Phone:</strong> (800) 555-2190</p>
                                                        <p><strong>Office:</strong> Executive Suite 14, 1100 Park Avenue</p>
                                                </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <form class="contact__form">
                                                <div class="form-grid">
                                                        <label>
                                                                <span>Name</span>
                                                                <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your full name" required />
                                                        </label>
                                                        <label>
                                                                <span>Email</span>
                                                                <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="you@company.com" required />
                                                        </label>
                                                        <label>
                                                                <span>Organization</span>
                                                                <input type="text" name="organization" placeholder="Hospital or health system" />
